      "text": [
        " آخِرِ اَلْعَشْرِ فَقَالَ «صُمِ اَلْأَوَّلَ فَلَعَلَّكَ لاَ تَلْحَقُ اَلثَّانِيَ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1799 - It is narrated that the Scholar, (Imam Musa ibn Jafar Al-Kadhim (as)), was asked about two Thursdays that occur in the last ten days of the month.\nImam (as) said: \"Fast the first one, for you may not live to see the second.\""
        ]
      }
